Frozen 2026-06-26 for the MCP epic — automated releases paused until it lands.

This marker pauses the two AUTOMATED release paths so mid-epic merges to main do
not accumulate into an auto-tagged release:

- release-please.yml  — skips opening/updating the rolling release PR.
- release-merge.yml    — the nightly cron skips readying + merging that PR.

Each workflow echoes this file's FIRST line in its skip notice, so keep line 1 a
concise, current reason.

